{"tid":1320912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：嚴厲譴責所有暴力示威者","createTime":"2019-07-15T13:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T16:30:19.000Z","uid":212626,"like":14,"dislike":494,"uniUserReply":131,"replies":[{"pid":"3555814576f70062fd9173b9a33d0aa33a0d7451","tid":1320912,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"沙田「反送中」遊行昨日結束後，警方與示威者晚上在新城市廣場發生衝突，雙方皆有人受傷送院。前特首兼全國政協副主席梁振英今日凌晨12時許在臉書發文，表示「慰問所有今晚被暴徒襲擊受傷的警察，嚴厲譴責所有暴力示威者」，是上月至今發生多宗反修例警民衝突後，梁振英首次回應。<br />\n<br />\n政府今年2月提出修例後，爭議越演越烈，梁振英至上月18日才於臉書首次評論修例爭議，指修例引致的風波重創香港在國外的聲譽，不過單靠中國駐外的使領館，以及力量單薄的香港特區經貿辦事處，「更不能靠外國傳媒」對外解釋說明，建議香港各大商會馬上組團連續出訪。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WPvkTwM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWPvkTwM.png&h=4d488090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/280972/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F280972%2F&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=93f0be78\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/280972/</a>"},{"pid":"9bf9216e2da203d1a722fd911767153403db299e","tid":1320912,"uid":212626,"like":10,"dislike":390,"score":-380,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ojRDFco.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FojRDFco.png&h=8f96ed0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b28b8c239ea0a7c23ed4b3136615a764425ee6a2","tid":1320912,"uid":113074,"like":239,"dislike":3,"score":236,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:48:37.000Z","msg":"拎曬所有官員嘅老婆出嚟組慰安團"},{"pid":"6c50ae12bd4bde8fdd8fbfe2e56115dafb0248cd","tid":1320912,"uid":39710,"like":265,"dislike":0,"score":265,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:48:56.000Z","msg":"玩少陣FB啦死仆街"},{"pid":"d160061ca87012dc2f7c37e76a13711a5008478a","tid":1320912,"uid":87272,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:49:10.000Z","msg":"咩身分呀"},{"pid":"9fe30d077aeadf8306ed76b07f0736f6dfe998fb","tid":1320912,"uid":5